Subject: [PATCH] stock management, user order cancellation, and dashboard
 order stats

- Add stock validation before adding to cart and placing orders
- Auto-decrement stock on order placement, restore on cancellation
- Add user cancel order endpoint (PATCH /api/orders/:orderId/cancel)
- Only allow cancellation for pending/confirmed orders
- Add order/revenue stats to admin dashboard endpoint
- Add recent orders and top selling products to stats

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
